PN,42901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FVolunteers from RAF Boulmer in
OL,8,FNorthumberland and the armed forces
OL,9,Fcharity, SSAFA, have joined forces to
OL,10,Fcreate a large sand artwork on Boulmer
OL,11,Fbeach to commemorate D-Day.
OL,13,FThe artwork, designed by the Soul2Sand
OL,14,Fartist Claire Eason, depicts the crest
OL,15,Fof RAF Boulmer intertwined with the
OL,16,Flogo of SSAFA.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FChair of SSAFA Northumberland,
OL,8,FCaroline Pryer, told ITV News: "It's
OL,9,Fvery special for Northumberland to be
OL,10,Fdoing something on the beaches,
OL,11,Freflecting D Day itself.
OL,13,F"Its very important for us, in all
OL,14,Fweathers, to know that our forces have
OL,15,Ffought in all weathers, and so our
OL,16,Fopportunity to reflect on them, and
OL,17,Freflect on the fallen and those who
OL,18,Fdid survive is very important."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FWarrant Officer Martin Dickson, from
OL,8,FRAF Boulmer, masterminded the project
OL,9,Fand said locating the artwork on the
OL,10,Fbeach is very symbolic when we
OL,11,Fremember those who fell during D-Day.
OL,13,FHe said: "The reason we've done sand
OL,14,Fart and we're waiting for the tide to
OL,15,Fcome in, is because as the sand
OL,16,Freclaims the sand art we can see that
OL,17,Fthe sand art is temporary. Just like
OL,18,Fmemories, they pass, but what we
OL,19,Fshould do is, obviously, remember the
OL,20,Flegacy of the veterans who have gone
OL,21,Fbefore us."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FThe volunteers battled through the wet
OL,8,Fweather on Wednesday (3 June) to
OL,9,Fcreate the artwork, having to restart
OL,10,Ftwice following heavy downpours.
OL,12,FBut artist Claire Eason said the
OL,13,Fchallenges were nothing compared to
OL,14,Fwhat the military faced on D-Day 82
OL,15,Fyears ago.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FShe said: "There've been lots of
OL,8,Fchallenges today, especially the
OL,9,Fweather, and for us, this is a tiny
OL,10,Ffraction of what was experienced on D
OL,11,FDay, and a little reminder to all of
OL,12,Fus of the sacrifices that were made
OL,13,Fand the stresses, the worry, the fear,
OL,14,Fand although we've had a few struggles
OL,15,Ftoday, it's been tiny in comparison."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1781187095
OL,3,CRAF personnel and SSAFA volunteers
OL,4,Ccreate sand artwork for D-Day
OL,5,Ccommemorations
OL,7,FFlight Sergeant Laura Rowberry
OL,8,Fvolunteered during the creation of the
OL,9,Fartwork and said it was a moving day
OL,10,Ffor all, adding: "It's really
OL,11,Fimportant that we look back and
OL,12,Fcommemorate these events, you know,
OL,13,Fthe 82nd anniversary of D-Day is
OL,14,Freally important, and this day has
OL,15,Fbeen really special to think about
OL,16,Fpeople who are currently serving,
OL,17,Fcurrently overseas as well and what
OL,18,Fsupport they will need in the future."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
